title: Cheers Fuckers St Patrick's Day Funny Men Beer Drinking Mugs T-Shirt
features: • Cheers Fuckers Funny St Patricks Day Beer Clothing Gifts. Distressed vintage drinking graphic apparel design showing beer mugs and green lucky shamrock leaf or clover. This makes a great costume party outfit for drinking squad or team to wear at the pub.
• Saint Patrick's Day novelty clothes for Irish men and women who love to drink on St Pattys Day or St Paddys Day Festival in Ireland.
• Lightweight, Classic fit, Double-needle sleeve and bottom hem
